You must specify a device.

Usage: ntfscp [options] device src_file dest_file

    -a, --attribute NUM   Write to this attribute
    -i, --inode           Treat dest_file as inode number
    -f, --force           Use less caution
    -h, --help            Print this help
    -m, --min_fragments   Do minimal fragmentation
    -N, --attr-name NAME  Write to attribute with this name
    -n, --no-action       Do not write to disk
    -q, --quiet           Less output
    -t, --timestamp       Copy the modification time
    -V, --version         Version information
    -v, --verbose         More output

